      <title>即使通胀降温，南非仍将延长利率暂停时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/south-africa-inflation-slows-on-easing-food-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于食品价格上涨较为温和，南非通胀率连续第二个月下降。]]></description>
