      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 08:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度尼西亚保持关键利率，衡量下一步行动的数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/indonesia-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-as-pressure-on-rupiah-abates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼央行行长佩里·瓦尔吉约 (Perry Warjiyo) 表示，印尼下一步的货币政策举措仍将由数据驱动，尽管上个月的加息在吸引外国资金和支撑卢比方面取得了初步成果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/indonesia-keeps-key-rate-unchanged-as-pressure-on-rupiah-abates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 07:29:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员越来越多地看到英国央行降息落后于欧洲央行，英镑上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/pound-rallies-traders-pare-bets-on-rate-cuts-after-uk-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国通胀放缓幅度低于预期，英国央行可能推迟降息，英镑兑欧元汇率升至两个多月来最高水平。]]></description>
